Opens Caſe and diſcovers a black deform'd Chineſe Joſs.
There's No1. —I never ſaw a greater beauty; it's enough to frighten one to look at it▪ what awe it inſpires! ay, ay, this is the pride of my intended ſon-in-law; he's fonder of this than the whole female race, now Heartwell's a fool; fond of nothing but wine, women, and ſuch trumpery—no ſenſe, no taſte—Now if the other be but as great a curioſity—if No. 2.
